    "Similarly, we sample episodes from D test during the testing stage to test whether the model can generalize well to new classes.",
    "Finally, we evaluate the average performance across all testing episodes.Episodic training is commonly employed in few-shot learning, where an episode T = {S, Q} can be viewed as a mini-batch.",
    "Hence, the training process of an episode is a batch training process.",
    "The training stage can be formulated asT train = {T i } Mtrain i=1, and the testing stage can be formulated asT test = {T i } Mtest i=1, where M train and M test denote the number of training episodes and testing episodes, respectively.",
    "MethodAn overview of the proposed MPC-CA method is illustrated in Fig. 3."
